## 1. Install QGIS
Download and install QGIS from [https://qgis.org](https://qgis.org).

## 2. Draw Your AOI
1. Open QGIS and create a new project.
2. Use the **Polygon tool** to outline your desired area (forest, city, etc.).
3. Save the layer as a **GeoJSON file**.

